{"tid":1940072,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"半年搵唔到工 就黎跳樓死","createTime":"2020-03-23T13:46:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-08T10:49:05.000Z","uid":311616,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"085a7d8977318db0783420fe52bc4bedad6312ed","tid":1940072,"uid":311616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T13:46:17.000Z","msg":"借朋友acc上黎呻下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n運動初期罷工罷到公司啲人屌我 後來我辭職果時仲拖我糧<br />\n點知辭撚完職就搵唔番份穩定工作<br />\n自己本身仲咩緊好多債 呢半年靠啲散工吊住條命<br />\n上網日日搵到好多地方都話請人 留電話叫人ws佢<br />\n點知果啲一係唔覆機 一係就九秒九話請左人<br />\n而家啲追數電話日日都係咁打黎 朋友借得既都借左<br />\n屋企人同得差唔多一樣咁窮幫唔到我 <br />\n我真係好撚無助 無學歷做唔到啲好好搵既工<br />\n而家連普普通通既工都搵唔到 真係好想跳樓算撚數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35e61763b59b256d0923c7cac1018cb646cd054a","tid":1940072,"uid":220787,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T13:49:43.000Z","msg":"做步兵搵餐晏仔先囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"804d684f15b7a45abb9b7b6edbc2a9d295e35b50","tid":1940072,"uid":311616,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"35e61763b59b256d0923c7cac1018cb646cd054a","tid":1940072,"uid":220787,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T13:49:43.000Z","msg":"做步兵搵餐晏仔先囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T13:51:49.000Z","msg":"唔明呀ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咩係步兵"},{"pid":"28fb469bb0cb2c57ff1fb5fbf2cb04ff7073cd73","tid":1940072,"uid":220787,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"804d684f15b7a45abb9b7b6edbc2a9d295e35b50","tid":1940072,"uid":311616,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"35e61763b59b256d0923c7cac1018cb646cd054a","tid":1940072,"uid":220787,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T13:49:43.000Z","msg":"做步兵搵餐晏仔先囉<img src=\"/a